939
00:07:06,990 --> 00:07:12,340
お前だけは 父上とその娘を 忘れないでいて

940
00:07:07,150 --> 00:07:11,280
I want you to remember my father and his daughter.

941
00:07:11,280 --> 00:07:12,370
I want you to remember my father and his daughter.

