1506
00:13:34,280 --> 00:13:36,170
でも城がぼろいのは

1507
00:13:34,290 --> 00:13:40,380
But I heard the castle is in shambles
due to your rampages as a young man.

1508
00:13:36,170 --> 00:13:40,610
